OL,7,FA Devon and Cornwall Police Constable
OL,8,Fwho used a vulnerable 81-year-old
OL,9,Fwoman's bank card to fraudulently make
OL,10,Fseveral purchases will be barred from
OL,11,Fpolicing.
OL,13,FPC Sam Smith was convicted of eight
OL,14,Fcounts of fraud and sentenced to 20
OL,15,Fmonths in prison at Exeter Crown Court
OL,16,Fin November 2023. He has been found
OL,17,Fguilty of gross misconduct following
OL,18,Fthe conviction and will be barred from
OL,19,Fpolicing.
