OL,7,FThe hearing found that, had Smith
OL,8,Fstill been a serving officer, he would
OL,9,Fhave been dismissed without notice.
OL,11,FSmith, aged 31, was working as a
OL,12,FPolice Constable in South Devon at the
OL,13,Ftime of the offences, which happened
OL,14,Fwhile he was off-duty.
OL,16,FThe hearing heard how Smith attended a
OL,17,Freport of concern for the welfare of
OL,18,Fthe victim in November 2019 and
OL,19,Fsubsequently befriended her.
