OL,7,FHe then made eight fraudulent
OL,8,Fpurchases with her bank card, without
OL,9,Fher knowledge or consent, between 30
OL,10,FMarch and 25 August 2020.
OL,12,FTemporary Deputy Chief Constable Dave
OL,13,FThorne said: "Sam Smith's appalling
OL,14,Factions involved a vulnerable victim
OL,15,Fand he was rightly convicted and
OL,16,Fjailed for these criminal offences.
