OL,7,F"There is no place within policing for
OL,8,Fthis unacceptable behaviour and our
OL,9,Fdetermination of gross misconduct was
OL,10,Fthe right, and only, appropriate
OL,11,Foutcome.
OL,13,F"All police officers have a privileged
OL,14,Frole in being part of a Force
OL,15,Fresponsible for the safeguarding of
OL,16,Fvulnerable people.
OL,18,F"Devon & Cornwall Police takes any
OL,19,Freports of illegal or inappropriate
OL,20,Fconduct extremely seriously.
